HEADWORD: Rubricate
<hw>Ru"bri*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rubricatus</ets> p. p. of <ets>rubricare</ets> to color red. See
<er>Rubric</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>Marked with red.</def>
